<h2 id="orga38a7da"><a id="orgfef8c65"></a> Research</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orga38a7da">
<p>
My research is in arithmetic geometry, the intersection of number theory and algebraic geometry. My interests gravitate toward problems in arithmetic statistics.
</p>
